Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, what are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what you and \Nyour friends need the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think what Luffy-kun \Nreally needs now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...to get his body and mind healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But my friends will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think they will \Ntry to get to Sabaody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The news about you has spread \Nall over the world already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it has reached your friends by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I have to see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised them. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here's my second suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On the small Sky Island - Weatheria, \Nwhere scientists study the weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...tried to escape from this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She suddenly disappeared \Nfrom the Weather Field
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and showed up at the Balloon Terminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she hijacked a balloon \Ncarrying a heavy load!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?! It's out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What's wrong with this balloon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Run fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no clue that she'd \Ndo something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what made her do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.37,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Crime"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! I'll give you back what I took!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Haredas-san... Call Haredas-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you out! We don't \Nknow what you'd do next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How should we punish this young girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A sentence of flooding or lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You common cat burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Hey, hey! Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Haredas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, hey, young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're really in a rage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This can help. Let me show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These are tightly tied Wind Knots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Haredas!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "let me out"! You want \Nanother one?! I'm in hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Haredas! Can you hear us?! Mr. Haredas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Haredas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She hit him rather than \Ntalk to him! She's a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Call the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She stole Weather Balls from the \NWeather Field and our research notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see here, Mr. Haredas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a thief and I'm a pirate now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the worst kind of human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have such a villain in our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said... I wanna \Nget out of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go now! You got \Nback what I stole, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too close! She's very violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to hijack the balloon and \Ngo down to the sea, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amateurs can't operate a \Nballoon. You could have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were very eager to learn \Nthe science of weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in that newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Luffy" in that newspaper \Nis the captain of our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They said he caused quite \Na stir in the previous war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a hot rookie with a Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I never would have thought \Nthat this boy was your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After his crew was separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy must've been fighting \Nsuch a hard battle on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And he took part in the Paramount War \Nin order to rescue Ace, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...he saw Ace killed right before his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't even... know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Luffy will be there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,at the place where we promised to meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he is completely broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see him and support him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, hey, hey, young girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so violent! We abducted \Na young girl and made her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Give the key to Mr. Haredas!\N--The key, the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can come out now. \NI'm sorry, young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where did she go?\N--I don't see Mr. Haredas, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How did she make it that far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She pretended to cry and now \Nshe took Mr. Haredas hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And she took the stolen goods, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,--We can't let her get away!\N--Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Weatheria's science of \Nweather must be kept secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care where! Please \Ntake me down to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--That's impossible...\N--Make it possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! I know that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!-- You've always supported us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our chance to return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch her! Don't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, young girl, you haven't \Nstop pretending to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, on the Winter \NIsland Future Land Baldimore
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,where the genius Vegapunk was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Grandpa! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Geek! Geek! Geek! Geek! Geek! \NGeek! Geek! Geek! Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kitton?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the old man has become \Nanother person again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like a demon this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:15:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you put something strange \Nin his stomach, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like habanero juice or kimchi soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go see my friend as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a ship... A ship to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we don't have a ship on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a liner that brings \Nus supplies once a month
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and Navy ships that come irregularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When is the liner due?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It just came a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I gotta wait for 3 weeks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This country is surrounded by thick \Nice. It's like a natural fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to get here, you need an \Nice-breaker with special equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can build a new ship but \Nit'll take too much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ol-Old man, you need to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good smell... Flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get off of this island at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With all that he's going through now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you have a good \Nreason but nothing can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an \Nice-breaker developed by Vegapunk at his laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it years ago, so I don't \Nknow if it still works...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's too dangerous! \NI'm not gonna go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that place again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Again"? Don't tell me \Nthat you snuck in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah, a while ago.\N--Uh-huh, a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can repair it! Because I'm a shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that's not what I'm concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's breaking into \NDr. Vegapunk's laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use any firearms inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that you're surrounded by \Npriceless treasures! Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I didn't expect Navy soldiers here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They tightened the security after I broke in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure? That laboratory?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Vegapunk works for the Navy \Nas head of all the sciences
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and we feel proud of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can say that his \Nbrain is a world-class treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where Vegapunk spent his boyhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at that mountain. \NIt has an odd shape, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It does when I come to \Nthink of it... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something he made when he was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to help the people in this \Ncountry from severe cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He converted animals in the forest \Ninto a work force and almost finished it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an earth heating system that \Nwill warm the whole island up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But as with many of his ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he couldn't make what was in his head real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't enough technology \Nor money to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But seeing him sad that he \Ncouldn't make everyone happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...warmed our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super tearjerking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We are always waiting for him to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't ever go into \Nthe laboratory with the self-destruct button.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just throw out the name of \Nthe most unwanted button in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say old man, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home and drink hot tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the only place \Nthat has an ice-breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which I need to get off of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just learned the news \Nof my captain's ordeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye! Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't ever push the \Nself-destruct button!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he \Nput one in in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just saw somebody! \NIt's this way! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the ice-breaker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, somebody broke into the laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a blueprint from there is priceless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I outran them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To all soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you break something in the \Ngenius Vegapunk's house while in pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--...it's a breach of the criminal code!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all super brilliant! I can't believe \Nthese are all from his younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of these ideas would need a couple \Nhundred years to implement fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right. As an engineer, I \Ndon't wanna mess with anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a pirate mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something? If I \Npush that button by any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it gonna be my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident on the Future Land
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,will be known around the world \Nas Baldimore's nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After hearing about the Paramount War,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro races full-tilt toward the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihawk watches him approach with cool eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What will come of their reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Luffy sets a huge plan in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Contact! The Great Swordsman, Mihawk\NZoro's Obstinate Struggle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
